videos.description: Stephen A. Smith says that James Harden certainly "showed up" but overall the Rockets' play was predictable and the Warriors were prepared.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Analysis (Stephen A.: Rockets were too predictable) 2018/05/14 ESHEET SC

videos.headline: Stephen A.: Rockets were too predictable

videos.description: Steph Curry explains why the Warriors were able to force so many turnovers and lauds Kevin Durant's ability to score.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Curry says no one in NBA may be able to guard Durant) 2018/05/14

videos.headline: Curry says no one in NBA may be able to guard Durant

videos.description: Draymond Green claims he was "amped up" at the start of Game 1 and was proud of his team to withstand the Rockets' strong start.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Presser (Draymond: I'd rather be overzealous than flat to start game) 2018/05/14

videos.headline: Draymond: I'd rather be overzealous than flat to start game

videos.description: Klay Thompson says Kevin Durant is the best player in the NBA at getting a good shot no matter who is guarding him.

videos.headline: Klay calls KD 'unstoppable' when in a zone

videos.description: Steph Curry says there will be a lot of "back and forth" based off the Rockets' game plan in the opening matchup of the Western Conference finals.
